RelatedSentence: IOWA CITY , Iowa - Iowa City Police are investigating after people reported that several shots were fired in the 2100 block of Davis Street around 7:30 p.m. Sunday .
Officers who arrived first on the scene found several shell casings in the roadway .
No injured people were found on Davis Street and police say they do n't know whether or not someone was hurt in this shooting .
